thread.title: Sarah Steiner

author: Sarah Steiner
title: Sarah Steiner
text: The representatives were very knowledgeable and answered all my questions. I currently was insured that was paying a higher premium but I knew I had good coverage, they found me the exact same coverage for $23 less per month and I shirred me that that was good for a year. I was told they will call me within a year and we will review my coverage to see if there are any better deals available I appreciate him keeping me up-to-date on what's out there
